3. Account Health (account_health.py) — B+
Lines: 3,862 | Role: KPIs, resource monitors, morning report
Strengths:
•	Executive Briefing is actionable and exportable
•	Morning Report pattern is unique and high-value for DBA teams
•	Scope metadata matching prevents stale data from wrong filters
•	get_session_for_action() gracefully handles offline mode
Weaknesses:
